    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several visible scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery shows noticeable wear and there are some minor stains on the carpet. While it remains a reliable daily driver, it would benefit from some cosmetic attention and a thorough detailing. Mechanically, it has been serviced regularly, though some minor non-essential components may require repair in the near future.",
